Job Descriptions
 Assist in tracking and reporting on available grants issued by the government
 Manage administrative matters related to grant calls, including submission and review of grant applications, and administration of post-award processes in adherence to terms and policies
 Liaise with internal and external partners to resolve queries and matters pertaining to grants
 Assist in compilation of data related to grants as part of internal and external reporting requirements
 Assist as needed in other supporting activities of the HR department

Job Requirements
 A bachelor뭩 degree
 Comfortable in handling simple statistics, numbers and datasets, or has equivalent quantitative background
 Experience with data manipulation or analysis such as Excel formulas
 Experience in budgets will be an advantage
 Good interpersonal skills and team player
 Excellent communication, analytic and writing skills